{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775857701766,"sessionID":"ses_286a23b06ffeA0T03gESJ1w8kY","part":{"id":"prt_d795e11d5001lxa4UrHgON671w","messageID":"msg_d795deca7001DJg2BEnsvGnc2d","sessionID":"ses_286a23b06ffeA0T03gESJ1w8kY","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-8350dbd4ba194260a38215b4e3de7499","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md","limit":100},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: 定义 AgentRuntime 自定义资源定义（CRD），用于在 Kubernetes 中声明 agent 运行时实例的配置和状态。\n6: \n7: ## Purpose\n8: \n9: 为 AgentCube 平台提供 AgentRuntime CRD 的 Go 类型定义，包括 API 组、版本、Schema 和 OpenAPI 验证规则。\n10: \n11: ## Module\n12: \n13: `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n14: \n15: ## Language\n16: \n17: Go 1.24\n18: \n19: ## Size\n20: \n21: S\n22: \n23: ## Scope\n24: \n25: ### In Scope\n26: \n27: 1. **AgentRuntime CRD 类型定义**\n28:    - `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` API 组\n29:    - Namespaced 作用域\n30:    - Go 结构体定义（Spec 和 Status）\n31:    - OpenAPIV3Schema 验证规则\n32:    - 默认值设置\n33:    - 打印列（Age）\n34: \n35: 2. **Required Spec 字段**\n36:    - `maxSessionDuration` (string, 默认 \"8h\")\n37:    - `sessionTimeout` (string, 默认 \"15m\")\n38:    - `targetPort` (TargetPort 数组)\n39:    - `podTemplate` (PodTemplateSpec)\n40: \n41: 3. **Status 字段**\n42:    - Conditions 集合\n43:    - 其他状态信息\n44: \n45: ### Out of Scope\n46: \n47: - Controller 实现\n48: - Webhook 验证\n49: - CRD YAML 生成（由 controller-gen 处理）\n50: - CodeInterpreter CRD（AR-002）\n51: \n52: ## Impact Analysis\n53: \n54: ### Components Impacted\n55: \n56: 1. **Workload Manager**\n57:    - 需要读取 AgentRuntime 资源\n58:    - 基于 AgentRuntime spec 创建 agent-sandbox Sandbox\n59:    - 更新 AgentRuntime status\n60: \n61: 2. **Client-Go Library**\n62:    - 生成的 TypedClient 包含 AgentRuntimeInterface\n63:    - Informer factory 支持 AgentRuntime 监听\n64:    - Lister 提供 AgentRuntime 查询\n65: \n66: 3. **Helm Chart**\n67:    - CRD YAML 在 `manifests/charts/base/crds/` 下\n68:    - CRD 随 chart 生命周期安装\n69: \n70: 4. **RBAC**\n71:    - WorkloadManager ClusterRole 包含 `agentruntimes` 的读权限\n72:    - `agentruntimes/status` 的更新权限\n73: \n74: ### Dependencies\n75: \n76: - `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/apiserver/v1alpha1` (或类似的基础类型)\n77: - `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1`\n78: - `k8s.io/api/core/v1` (用于 PodSpec 引用)\n79: \n80: ## Design Decisions\n81: \n82: ### API Group and Version\n83: \n84: **选择**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n85: \n86: **理由**:\n87: - 遵循 Kubernetes API 组命名约定（域名反转）\n88: - `v1alpha1` 表示早期版本，允许未来变更\n89: - 与 CodeInterpreter CRD 共享 API 组\n90: \n91: ### Spec Fields 设计\n92: \n93: **maxSessionDuration**\n94: - 类型: `string`\n95: - 默认值: `\"8h\"`\n96: - 用途: 单个 agent 会话的最大持续时间\n97: \n98: **sessionTimeout**\n99: - 类型: `string`\n100: - 默认值: `\"15m\"`\n\n(Showing lines 1-100 of 3902. Use offset=101 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义\n\n## Overview\n\n定义 AgentRuntime 自定义资源定义（CRD），用于在 Kubernetes 中声明 agent 运行时实例的配置和状态。\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 AgentCube 平台提供 AgentRuntime CRD 的 Go 类型定义，包括 API 组、版本、Schema 和 OpenAPI 验证规则。\n\n## Module\n\n`pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1`\n\n## Language\n\nGo 1.24\n\n## Size\n","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775857701727,"end":1775857701764}}}}
